overview: CHIKARA's war with the Flood continues, as Worker Ant battles his former GEKIDO ally deviANT, AC/DC face the CHIKARA Campeones de Parejas Pieces of Hate in a non-title match and the Spectral Envoy takes on the Wrecking Crew in trios action. Plus, the Baltic Siege continue their grudge with the Bloc Party, and more.
title: CHIKARA Quantum Of Solace
